data.description:
This charming home is nestled in the highly desirable Palm Grove subdivision, offering the added perk of no HOA. With an abundance of space and storage, this residence is perfect for those seeking room to grow.As you enter, you'll be greeted by a galley kitchen complete with a convenient pantry, making meal preparation a breeze. The living room boasts a stunning brick fireplace, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere for gatherings or relaxation.One of the highlights of this home is the enclosed Florida room, providing a serene retreat while offering panoramic views of the spacious fenced-in backyard. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee or hosting friends and family in this delightful space. The primary suite is a true sanctuary, featuring a walk-in closet and an en-suite bath, ensuring privacy and comfort. Additionally, the indoor laundry adds convenience to your daily routine.

With endless potential, this home is just waiting for your personal touch. Whether you envision modern updates or a classic design, embrace the endless possibilities this property has to offer.
